Not that I update this but..

Yesterday was my 7 month anniversary, I never imagined I would be with Brendan for 7 months.  Now I cant imagine my life without him.  

I love college.  Like, LOVE college.  I just wish Brendan and Steph were more availabe to me here.  

My parents are coming this weekend.  

I miss Steph and Brendan.  

I love my roommate.

We rearranged our room when everyone said it wasnt possible but were just that awesome.  And our room looks so pimp.

I LOVE TOWSON.

Today I got accepted to UNCW.  I got accepted to every college I applied to... not bad.  I wasn't really expecting that. yayyyyy

I apologize for the pointlessness of this entry

im happy.


i have a boyfriend.

im really happy.

i feel like shit right now.  no particular reason.  im trying so hard not to fall back into old bad habits. (my resolution)  i have a maybe worse bad habit now though.  uggghhhh.  I have a bad habit of ....... bad habits.  


my parents are making me lose at least 6 pounds by the end of the month.  ew.  im one of those people.  I hate that.  ew.  Im so grossed out.                   










fuck.

My heart beats so fast i get physically dizzy when i know youre near.  Its crazy how much i like you.  I hope I dont seem too creepy writing shit like this.  Ive had a few bad incidents with boys latley and im finally semi-happy.  I wish things could stay exactly like they are now.

Do you know I melted when you leaned over and wispered in my ear?  


Well, not wisper, kind of yelled over the music.  Still.  I m.e.l.t.e.d.

SOOO last night sucked.  boys= not fun.  anyways, the real reason im updating

I want to start making a group for beach week because in order to get a house were going to have to reserve it within the next couple months.  If you want to stay with me at beach week, lemme know, or if you know anyone else who is starting a group.  
thankss

Ten things that make you happy, no order. Five people that you want to hear back from.

1. chocolate chip cookie dough ice cream
2. when you know youre right
3. my bay house
4. catching a fish
5. flirting
6. SNOW DAYS
7. watching good movies
8. eating family dinners
9. online shopping
10. being with awesome friends

anyone who hasnt done it yet... consider yourself tagged

Tonights cast party sucked.  I hate how people treat me differently.  Why do I feel so seperate from everyone?  I wish that just once I could like a boy and just have him not like anyone.  He doesnt have to like me at all.  Just not someone else.  gaaaahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh.  I suck at boys.  I used to be so skilled, but now I am nothing but a SFCG.  And I feel like a havent been to crew in 21412534531425 years.  Crew makes me happy.  But - crew and + dissrespectful brother = not happy michelle.  

Oh.  I told you my mix sucked, so dont say I didnt warn you.

Joan Helen Furton

10/7/1930 - 11/29/05

Rest In Peace

Im feeling much better.  I have now gotten acceptance letters from 3 schools

Lenoir-Rhyne College

Towson University

UNC Greensboro

Thats beast.

Things with boys are kind of really good.  And by that I mean Im afraid Im going to screw it up by saying anything.  SO.  The only reason im updating is so that i dont have to go do my english paper.  Yay senioritis.  Its kind of hard to feel motivated when im allready accepted to 3 schools.  Yeah so Im going to go NOT fail english.



"WOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO"
"Thank God youre not leaving or else I would really cry"
Haha Davey

oh, any requests for DP mix 05??

Im in like.  like like like like like.  Im just really happy right now.  With everything.  Ive been clean for 15 days.  Woot for me.  If im going to do this clean thing i need your help.  Im happy.  YAY.  the end.

ok, Homecoming date... UNcheck.




Fuck.  I really do hate men.

Last night was really random/fun.  

I missed not hanging out with you.

Just once I'd like to be able to look in the mirror and see whats right with me.

It's never good enough, this needs fixing, that needs to go away, fill in the blanks...

I've become obsessed.

I'm disgusted with my body, my face, everything.

I'm disgusting.

Me, me me.

EDIT: my brother just knocked on my door and said, "sorry for calling you fat".  Maybe my family is starting to realize what the critisism has done to me.

Tomorrow were taking pictures with Fire Man and Nano Pup.  Its going to be real sad.  We layed Lily Baby to rest today.  Saying goodbye is so hard.  Im going to cry tomorrow.  It still hasnt fully hit me that Im going to be a senior.  (Graduation in 10 months).  Monday will be really wierd when all the babies come in to school all dumb.  Yay for hating people.  Yay for riding the bus too.  Ugh.  School.  Im going to miss Frank very dearly... not that hes going anywhere... I'm so in denial.  BLAH!

I'm empty inside.




          But I love it when a boy plays with my hair.

1 internship  aprill

4 honors english  price

I live for nights like tonight.

Here is a schedule for my summer:

Tomorrow I am leaving for Mifflinburg, PA.  Workcamp for 5 days.  Ill be back saturday then MONDAY JUNE 27th IS MY BIRTHDAY!!

July 10th- 13th college tour.


July 20th- August 3rd(about)  ITALY! Well for 3 days then a cruise.  Im sooooooo excited!!

Then warped tour and what not when I get back, but make sure all the people i want to chill with are home during the same days I am.  

Ill write about workcamp when I get back.  Have fun!

I have a hot date saturday ;)  


Im going to fail my precal exam because I havent studied at ALL, but i doubt i could get a b anyways


This weekend is going to kick ass

I am incredibly freaked out right now.  It just hit me that some of my best friends are recieving thier diplomas right now.  This is so strange.  My brain is finally starting to comprehend that in a week I will be  a senior in high school.  How did I get this old?  Where did the other 16 years of my life go?  ::Freaks out::


Im so wierded out right now.
MY SENIORS ARE BACK!!!! yayyyyyyy I am SO excited for this summer... :)

Today was a really fun walk to school.  First off, it was Keith, Christina, Michelle, and me.  So its raining  and Michelle and I are wearing like sandals, while walking across the crosswalk, I slipped, then grabbed on to her and then she slipped and we were both screaming.  I guess you had to be there.  But then we were walking and Christina's umbrella held a branch back and it let go and it flung and hit Michelle in the face.  It was really funny. I just thought I should share my funny story to brighten your day.  :)   MY SISTER COMES HOME IN LESS THAN 10 HOURS!!!!!1.  I dont know how I will be able to contain myself at school tomorrow knowing that shes at home.  Well at least I have a few conversations with a few people to look forward to.

Who knows how late one acts will run until?  Are they only on wednesday night?  Thats the one night this week im working.  Poo.   I dont want to miss one acts.  MY SISTER COMES HOME WEDNESDAY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

I'm in like.  ::BLUSH::






*sigh*
I like the way things are going boy-wise right now.  Not too happy about school though.  Eh, whatever.  I'm excited for Workcamp, like really excited.  This entry is weird, because I'm in a wierd mood.  Like does that  to a girl. hehe.   I'm going to go spin around in circles and frolic happily.  :)
Guess who just got her first job?? yay me!!!!
I love crew.  I love cast.  I love shows.  I am in such a loving mood (see weasel).  But seriously, tonights "cast party" was hot.  :) x 10^23

OKAY.  im really pissed now I just wrote a really long entry but it didnt post..... me and LJ arent friends anymore.   


Does anyone know how much I have to pay by thursday and who i write the check out to for the NYC trip??? thanks


Thursday is 4 months.

My last entry was so much better.

If you read this, even if I don't speak to you often, you must comment with a memory of me. It can be anything you want, it can be good or bad, just so long as it happened. Then post this to your journal. See what people remember about you.

Leave an anonymous comment with:
- One secret.
- One compliment.
- Lyrics to a song.
- How long we've been friends.
- And a hint to who you are.

im grounded.  as in no show, no cast party, no paper plates.



EDIT:  wow, I am amazing.  If anyone ever needs a lawyer, call me up because I am incredibly persuasive.  I have sucessfully traded my grounding for next weekend, so nobody have a party next Saturday.


::Brushes shoulders off::

this morning i was informed that Solomon King died.  In 7th and 8th grade we were really close and I used to go to his house.  it seems like many people lost touch with him once we started high school, but we still smiled at eachother in the halls and talked when we had the chance.  I cant believe hes gone.  16. that is way too young.  Nobody this close to me has died before, with the exception of Ian, but we saw that coming, and i dont know what to do.  This is shocking.  So tonight, turn on your wipers, turn down the music, pay attention, and try to watch out.  God Bless You Solomon.  I will always remember all the fun we had, I could never forget you, even if I tried.  Rest in Peace.

ok so today i didnt go to school because my throat hurts and i decided i needed a mental health day.  Yesderday was freakin awesome, right Sam??  

Being home all day while everyone is at school is boring so i was thinking what shall i do?? when all of a sudden i thought BLACK PEOPLE MUSIC!! That's right everyone i made a mix of 1 hour and 43 minutes of pure dance music, its all black people music, except for eminem, but he counts as black.  Its so good and i cant wait till we all get down and funky at our next get together.  

So besides making the best ghetto mix EVER, i have done nothing all day and i'm going to fail precal, but who said i need precal?  Well i'm going to listen to all my ghetto glory,

wow i havent updated in like 17 years.

but just in case youre oblivious to everything this weekend was kickass.

ive never had so much fun in my whole life and this year has just begun, i cant wait.  Next time wayy more kissing and way less awkwardness.  Agreed?  


I LOVE LIFE RIGHT NOW!!! :)

Today was really fun. I got out of bed because I had to throw up. I'm really sick. I mean REALLY sick. I feel sad, because Sarah and Britney are complete bitches. They told everyone I have an STD, just because I slept with both of their boyfriends on Saturday night. I'm so sad. My kitten got run over this afternoon. I found him when I was coming home from school. His head was all squished. I took some photos. I'll miss him. Poor kitty. Last night I had to finish my term paper on the history of pre-communist Russian society. I focussed on the needs of women. I think it's ok, but if I don't pass this I'll lose my scholarship. I want to tell the world that my girlfriend Amy is the bomb! She made pizza last night, and even though I burnt my lips on the cheese, it was awesome!!! I am updating this journal for the first time in ages, because I've been in prison. Today, I got a digital camera! Yes! Here's some photos of my cock. I want to say thanks to simon and Abbey and Dave and the other Simon for helping me on Saturday. You guys are the best. By the way, if you happen to find my wallet, keys or underwear, could you SMS me? Adrian has my number. I went to the doctor yesterday, and he said I have bipolar disorder, and a healthy imagination. You should all do this quiz! It's amazingly accurate. You just put in your name and birthday, and it will tell you you're a moron. hit parade tomorrow @ 7 30 be there or die im nervous That's enough for now. But I'll leave you with this poem I wrote. omggg i feel so bad.  i borrowed caitlins chapter package to copy.. i know it was wrong and ill never do it again, but i said i would give it to her after school, but when i came home i wasnt feeling well and slept and then i woke up when it was dark.  im soooooo sorry you dont even know.  if anyone knows where she goes in the morning or what she has first period i would appreciate it if you told me.  im so scared because now shes not able to study for her test and its all because i was too lazy to do it myself.  this is the first time i copied someone but still thats not an excuse.  i just cant stop thinking about it so everyone remind me to find caitlin.  and if youre reading this, im so sorry and i really dont want to wreck our friendship and i hope you can forgive me.  im done procrastinating and i will never copy or take someones work.  i am so sorry caitlin, i cant even express it in words.  please forgive me.
i feel like ive drifted so far away from my friends and im on a different island screaming my head off.  but they still cant hear me.
